Project Description
WPF Image Utils is a set of image related applications that use WPF. Currently the project focuses on a picture viewer

Currently the project has one application, a Picture viewer. A screencast of the application can be found here: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=su6RlVCuNUQ&hd=1
